	quest.07FA368632D7C5B6.quest_desc: [
		"Basic materials"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"All mechanisms in the mod are technically considered multi-block, meaning they consist of the machine itself (e.g., a centrifuge), a machine core, and add-ons (upgrades). Machine cores are installed on the machine (e.g., a centrifuge), and add-ons are installed on the core. There can be multiple cores and add-ons. To install cores, right-click the machine core, and the core will automatically install itself."
	]
