	quest.33E857D51356892C.quest_desc: [
		"Increases the maximum number of crafting stages by 1. Connects tightly to the \"&eRAM&r\" ME network."
		"{@pagebreak}"
		"Example:"
		"Cobblestone -> Gravel -> Sand - this is a two-step process. For this recipe, the network will first crush all the cobblestone required for crafting into gravel, and only then crush the gravel into sand. This means it will split the two-step crafting process into two single-step processes. However, if you install a processing unit, the network will not split the crafting process, but will perform both steps simultaneously."
	]
